<p sourcefile="ProcessDoku/02_SupportProcesses/02_01_Finance/organization-administration/configure-email.md" sourcestartlinenumber="52">On the <strong sourcefile="ProcessDoku/02_SupportProcesses/02_01_Finance/organization-administration/configure-email.md" sourcestartlinenumber="52">Email parameters</strong> page, note the following settings on the <strong sourcefile="ProcessDoku/02_SupportProcesses/02_01_Finance/organization-administration/configure-email.md" sourcestartlinenumber="52">SMTP settings</strong> tab.</p>
