<h3 id="workflow-email-notification-testing" sourcefile="ProcessDoku/02_SupportProcesses/02_01_Finance/organization-administration/configure-email.md" sourcestartlinenumber="252">Workflow email notification testing</h3>
<p sourcefile="ProcessDoku/02_SupportProcesses/02_01_Finance/organization-administration/configure-email.md" sourcestartlinenumber="254">The testing for email notifications is to simply trigger the notification and then check for it.</p>
<ol sourcefile="ProcessDoku/02_SupportProcesses/02_01_Finance/organization-administration/configure-email.md" sourcestartlinenumber="256">
<li sourcefile="ProcessDoku/02_SupportProcesses/02_01_Finance/organization-administration/configure-email.md" sourcestartlinenumber="256"><p sourcefile="ProcessDoku/02_SupportProcesses/02_01_Finance/organization-administration/configure-email.md" sourcestartlinenumber="256">Submit a workflow that has been set up for email notifications.</p>
</li>
<li sourcefile="ProcessDoku/02_SupportProcesses/02_01_Finance/organization-administration/configure-email.md" sourcestartlinenumber="257"><p sourcefile="ProcessDoku/02_SupportProcesses/02_01_Finance/organization-administration/configure-email.md" sourcestartlinenumber="257">Check the workflow history to make sure that a workflow work item was assigned to the expected user.</p>
</li>
<li sourcefile="ProcessDoku/02_SupportProcesses/02_01_Finance/organization-administration/configure-email.md" sourcestartlinenumber="258"><p sourcefile="ProcessDoku/02_SupportProcesses/02_01_Finance/organization-administration/configure-email.md" sourcestartlinenumber="258">Check the status of the pending email notification in <strong sourcefile="ProcessDoku/02_SupportProcesses/02_01_Finance/organization-administration/configure-email.md" sourcestartlinenumber="258">System administration</strong> &gt; <strong sourcefile="ProcessDoku/02_SupportProcesses/02_01_Finance/organization-administration/configure-email.md" sourcestartlinenumber="258">Periodic tasks</strong> &gt; <strong sourcefile="ProcessDoku/02_SupportProcesses/02_01_Finance/organization-administration/configure-email.md" sourcestartlinenumber="258">Email processing</strong> &gt; <strong sourcefile="ProcessDoku/02_SupportProcesses/02_01_Finance/organization-administration/configure-email.md" sourcestartlinenumber="258">Batch email sending status</strong>.</p>
<p sourcefile="ProcessDoku/02_SupportProcesses/02_01_Finance/organization-administration/configure-email.md" sourcestartlinenumber="260">If the email is fails to send, make sure that the SMTP mail account can be opened.</p>
</li>
